    <section name="Create new Mapping files">
      <p>
        The plugin provides a simple wizard for creating new mapping-xml files.
        A new mapping-xml file can be created using File > New > Other > Dozer Mapping Framework > Dozer Mapping File.
        Select the correct dozer version (4, DTD or 5, XSD) in the wizard and create the file.
